## Verification

- preview before apply when possible
- confirm the touched managed paths and concrete skill/agent selected

## Gotchas / Safety

- do not turn this into a daily wrapper ritual
- do not recommend vague pack umbrellas when a concrete skill exists
- keep managed exports additive and reversible
